{"tid":673081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【退出核協議】美向伊朗提「12條協議 」 警告施「史上最強制裁」","createTime":"2018-05-21T13:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T15:51:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81a7c7b808adf8bcde8bab2b5784d0a5cd07be26","tid":673081,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180521&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58221463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180521%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58221463&d=06Ej3lOb8dMH8tBioTijC%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9da38df8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180521%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D58221463&h=0bc6114c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180521&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=58221463</a><br />\n【退出核協議】美向伊朗提「12條協議 」 警告施「史上最強制裁」<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普早前宣佈退出在2015年達成的伊朗核協議後，美國國務卿蓬佩奧周一呼籲伊朗與美國達成新的核協議，其中美方提出12項條件，蓬佩奧警告伊朗政府若不改變現時做法，美方將會施加「史上最強制裁」。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧提出的12項條件，包括伊朗停止提煉濃縮鈾、停止預先處理鈈元素，以及容許專家檢查伊朗全國任何地方。此外，蓬佩奧亦要求伊朗從敍利亞撤走部隊，不再支持也門的胡塞叛軍，以及釋放所有在囚的美國公民。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧稱，如果伊朗作出「重大改變」，美國願意撤銷所有制裁，並恢復雙方全面的外交及商業關係。"},{"pid":"8d132bc50f601b918447204543cb36d1a225bedb","tid":673081,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"如果侵仔對 Chi Na 咁有決心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e16acd47e79e0d8e0290523405e3d725c8b652","tid":673081,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d132bc50f601b918447204543cb36d1a225bedb","tid":673081,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"如果侵仔對 Chi Na 咁有決心就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}